description: Eastside one bedroom with deeded off street parking space. Outstanding location at the intersection of East Fourth Street and L Street in the Tuckerman School House condos. Convenient to the MBTA bus stops 7,9, 10 and 11. Easy access to all of downtown Boston, Logan International and Rts 90 and 93. Very well cared for and established condo association. Pride of ownership is evident throughout the property. This home is a one bedroom garden level condo with spacious living room and bedroom, galley kitchen and full bathroom. This home features a private enclosed patio area and private entrance directly into the home.
